  <subsection>
    <title>Disability Accommodations</title>
    <p>
      Students needing testing or classroom accommodations based on a disability are encouraged to discuss those needs with me as soon as possible.
      Please see <url href="https://www.latech.edu/ods" visual="">Office of Disability Services</url> website for more information.
    </p>
  </subsection>

  <subsection>
    <title>Counseling</title>
    <p>
      Information, contact numbers, and sites for Louisiana Tech Counseling Services are located on their <url href="https://www.latech.edu/current-students/student-advancement-affairs/counseling-services/" visual="">website</url>.
    </p>
  </subsection>

